title: #92Noon LIVE from Training Camp! Weatherly/Bercich/Wobby/Wilf/Stefanski/Coleman
description: It's another 92Noon broadcast live from TCO Performance Center in Eagan for the Minnesota Vikings Training Camp! Vikings DE Stephen Weatherly stops by the perch, the Vikings Radio Network's Greg Coleman and Pete Bercich swing by, Vikings President Mark Wilf shares his excitement for the upcoming season, and Wobby makes his regular appearance!
